svasti śrī {meykkīrtti}

{meykkīrtti} koppara {layer of black grease} Uttuṅka  nāṭākiya kuṉṟakkūṟṟattu brahmadeyam ciṟupaḻuvūr tiruvālantuṟaiy Āḻvār nilamThe -la was added under the –m, perhaps because it had been forgotten. coṟṟi kuṭuttu ‡ pāṇṭārattu ‡ Irinta kācil Ikkoyil śrī koyiluṭaiyom koṇṭa kācu 15 Ikkācu patiṉ Aiñtum koṇṭu comittāl ne ‡ yyamutu ‡ potu

Oru piṭiyāka nicatam muppiṭi neyyamutu ce[y]taru[ḷa] {layer of black grease} [Itu]cantradityaval panmāheśvara rakṣai ||
